Shelly Burch https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shelly_Burch 0 Shelly Burch (born March 19, 1960) is an American actress and singer known to television audiences for her role as Delila Ralston on ABC's daytime soap opera One Life to Live, a role she played for eight years.
